igins. <strong>Explore </strong>the stars, <strong>Evolve </strong>your army and <strong>Fight </strong>an alien threat. <strong>Choose </strong>to help characters or harm them - will you be <strong>Feared</strong>, <strong>Admired</strong>, or <strong>Respected</strong>?",
